y%2F1209&d=iBLSwy1tqwhlDNpwtuM9DSukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=bd81a9f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a><br />\n官方link (我們香港人計劃) :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2F&d=iBLSwy1tqwhlDNpwtuM9DSukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=f3957c60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/</a><br />\n.<br />\n(對唔住，雖然區選迎來短暫的勝利，但要做ge 野都要持績落去，唔好放軟手腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，手足，星期四愛丁堡見)"},{"pid":"a00daa994b0a8b3e32f7c7ab75f52b36b990907d","tid":1759192,"uid":130343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a058ff5f88dfdfbcf9321163d65b629368bbf8d","tid":1759192,"uid":302976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"991fc794ffb28a0f58e11d0e136437b75b8a8cba","tid":1759192,"uid":130343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"315eba7c4e8a6fccdccb619139cbe9c657fb034f","tid":1759192,"uid":302976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T13:36:09.000Z","msg":"好想去，嗰心囉囉攣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T13:39:14.000Z","msg":"等雨 呢幾日會收到 我都係今日收到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T13:39:58.000Z","msg":"唉屌，我好似唔記得比申請文件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T13:40:31.000Z","msg":"佢要你sd email俾身分證 passport 個啲"},{"pid":"874cac60ff67aa722026737c2871bc5c9d50f6d7","tid":1759192,"uid":302976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a00daa994b0a8b3e32f7c7ab75f52b36b990907d","tid":1759192,"uid":130343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a058ff5f88dfdfbcf9321163d65b629368bbf8d","tid":1759192,"uid":302976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"991fc794ffb28a0f58e11d0e136437b75b8a8cba","tid":1759192,"uid":130343,"like":0,"